    "biography": {
      "value": "<p>The Rootgnaw Queen is a massive blighted insectoid that nests deep beneath the corrupted roots of the Ashen Woods. Her chitinous carapace drips with caustic acid and her mandibles can crush armour like kindling. Where she burrows, the ground cracks and heaves, and her brood of grubs follows in her wake.</p>",
      "director": "<p>The Rootgnaw Queen is an elite — she acts twice per round (once on her initiative, once on initiative count 0). Use Mandible Crush to grab a frontliner, then Acid Spray to create difficult terrain that splits the party. Burrow Surge lets her reposition without provoking. Brood-Mother spawns 2 grubs each round to swarm isolated PCs. Use Seismic Tremor (boss action) to knock the party prone and create more difficult terrain. Root-Sense means she always knows where PCs are — no sneaking past her.</p>",
